{"tid":792006,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓媒指支韓泳手發生肢體衝突　中方道歉南韓考慮申訴","createTime":"2018-08-24T08:53:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-24T09:00:13.000Z","uid":51271,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1ff16415c9cdac1213976ffdb0f71038cb89bea1","tid":792006,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T08:53:48.000Z","msg":"南韓傳媒報道，南韓女子蛙泳選手金海津，在亞運會熱身期間，意外撞到一名中國游泳選手的面部，金海津隨即向她道歉，但被對方腳踢襲擊。<br />\n<br />\n報道指，兩國教練事發後迅速分隔二人，防止事態升級，中方人員向南韓教練和運動員道歉，其後再到亞運村向南韓代表團致歉，報道沒有透露涉事中國運動員的身份。<br />\n<br />\n南韓代表團指，考慮向奧林匹克評議會提出申訴，強調體育絕對不允許暴力行為，即使中國泳手已經道歉，亦必須接受公正處罰<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414343-20180824.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414343-20180824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=itMRmcMEBhBK6NMbRZTM%2BKEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=deecafce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1414343-20180824.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=83198122\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1414343-20180824.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"ba4ddf3b44b9091166e7f613910bbe5def498f61","tid":792006,"uid":2419,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-24T09:00:13.000Z","msg":"dq all<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}